body:
Captain Marvel Spoiler! Lietenant Trouble

Right, so I am 99% sure that Monica Rambeau, also known as Lietenant Trouble will be true to her word and have built her own space ship in Avengers Endgame. I also think that, like her mom, she would have established herself as a kick ass pilot. Now I can’t wait to see her and Captain Marvel reunite. Girls be ready to go further higher faster baby.
